  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Gravitational Force
Formula: F = Gm1m2/r²
Note:    Universal gravitation between all masses

Domain:  Geology
Topic:   Age of Earth
Formula: 4.54 billion years
Note:    Determined by radiometric dating of oldest rocks/meteorites

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Age of Universe
Formula: 13.8 billion years
Note:    Determined by CMB and Hubble constant measurement

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Boyle's Law
Formula: P₁V₁ = P₂V₂
Note:    Pressure and volume inversely proportional at constant T

Domain:  Medicine
Topic:   Human Genome
Formula: ~3 billion base pairs; ~20,000 genes
Note:    Completed Human Genome Project 2003

